'''Ubuntu TV'''是一款由[[Canonical|Canonical]]開發的[[智能電視|智能電視]][[作業系統|作業系統]]，基於[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]開發，並統一了界面。<ref name=theverge /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/247571/canonical_demonstrates_ubuntu_tv.html |title=Canonical Demonstrates Ubuntu TV |publisher=Pcworld.com |date= |accessdate=11 January 2012 |archive-date=2012-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413111501/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/247571/canonical_demonstrates_ubuntu_tv.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcadvisor.co.uk/new-product/ces/3328531/ces-canonical-shows-off-ubuntu-tv/ |title=CES: Canonical shows off Ubuntu TV |publisher=Pcadvisor.co.uk |date=19 December 2011 |accessdate=11 January 2012 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220021502/http://www.pcadvisor.co.uk/new-product/ces/3328531/ces-canonical-shows-off-ubuntu-tv/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.itproportal.com/2012/01/10/canonical-ubuntu-tv-surfaces-ces-2012/ |title=Canonical’s Ubuntu TV Surfaces at CES 2012 |publisher=Itproportal.com |date= |accessdate=11 January 2012 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107113107/https://www.itproportal.com/2012/01/10/canonical-ubuntu-tv-surfaces-ces-2012/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2014年10月，還沒有任何產品搭載這個系統，也沒有發佈給公眾使用。

==特色==
Ubuntu TV基於Ubuntu 12.04開發，擁有錄製和播放[[DVD-Video|DVD-Video]]與[[Blu-ray|Blu-ray]]影片的能力，還有可從[[電腦|電腦]]傳輸影音檔案到其他終端的功能。

